AST Halong Bay Tours
Nov 2013 ‚Ä¢ Family
Halong Bay is one of the most beautiful places on earth. No trip to Vietnam is complete without going there. We took a 2-3 star tour with AST. The guide, Hoi, was excellent. We booked through Hanoi Backpackers Hostel for convenience, although you can save 20% by doing it on your own. You should do 3 day 2 night if time permits. Cat Ba island was more interesting than bungalow option unless you want romantic atmosphere. Sadly, garbage abounds in the water and unless Vietnamese government steps in this place will be ruined.
