Wonder of the World
Aug 2012 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Halong Bay is simply stunning. Everything about it is incredible. I'd only recommend a 1 night cruise because you can see it all in that time. Definitely see the "Suprising, Amazing Cave" or whatever they call it. It is both of those things! The water is bioluminescent, so at night you can toss water or rocks into the water and watch it light up like fireworks! I'd splurge on a balcony room so you can relax and enjoy the view while you cruise around. Just be sure to go in the summer when it's warm!!!
